text Hello there, and welcome to StoryBuilder!
text This is just a quick template to demenstrate some of the various features of this engine.

writemode let+LET true "You can only enter letters here" cancel:loop
write name "What is your name."
text Hello "<name>". Nice to meet you!

writemode num+let+LET true "You can only enter letters and numbers here" cancel:continue
write name2 "What is your nickname, optional."
if name2 != ""
    text That's a nice nickname! From now on, I'll call you "<name2>".
endif

writemode num true "You can only enter numbers here" cancel:continue
write age "What is your age, optional."
if age != ""
    text Oh wow! For being "<age>" years old, you still managed to get it in you to write down your name. Nice job!
endif

text This ends the demenstration. Goodbye!
end
